modules.description: Handles HTTP communication with TLS encryption using Cohttp and Tls, supporting request sending and response parsing. Operates on HTTP messages, headers, and connection states. Enables secure API interactions and web service communications over encrypted channels.

Provides functions for handling TLS errors and creating HTTP clients with authentication and caching. Works with X509 authentication structures, certificate files, and Lwt-based asynchronous operations. Used to establish secure HTTP connections with custom certificate validation and debug logging.
